\/view\\/',NULL,'','2013-11-14','2013-11-14','http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/soltech-solar-panel-glass-roof-designboom01.jpg@@##http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/soltech-solar-panel-glass-roof-designboom021.jpg@@##http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/soltech-solar-panel-glass-roof-designboom04.jpg@@##http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/soltech-solar-panel-glass-roof-designboom05.jpg@@##http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/soltech-solar-panel-glass-roof-designboom06.jpg@@##http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/soltech-solar-panel-glass-roof-designboom07.jpg@@'),(148,'jakob gomez: 多用gibooth椅',' ## ## ##\r\n由墨西哥设计师jakob gomez设计的“gibooth”椅子可以轻松地适应多种环境，不管是居家或办公，都能为使用者提供灵活的\r\n空间布局。巨大的耳罩椅背设计提供了高级的隔音效果，这个设计不仅能满足个人集中注意力的工作，还适用于几组人的\r\n讨论互动——非常适合开放的工作空间。椅子由三种不同的木板制作，有几款基本颜色可供选择。这个1平方米的椅子，\r\n用这种壁龛一样的形式将工作与娱乐、公共与私密相结合。## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ##\r\n这个设计来自于designboom的专栏\'DIY submissions\'，我们欢迎广大读者积极投稿，上传自己的设计作品。\r\n浏览更多读者投稿请点击这里。','http://cn.designboom.com/cat/4/view/1936/jakob-gomez-%E5%A4%9A%E7%94%A8gibooth%E6%A4%85.html','--- !ruby/object:Nokogiri::XML::Element {}\n','',1,2,13,'boom_cn',NULL,'\\/view\\/',NULL,'','2013-11-14','2013-11-14','http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/dbsub/375274/2013-08-20/img_1_1376968191_8e78fcfd8213ccf7e874b79890e93445.jpg@@jakob gomez\'s gibooth chair offers flexible solutions\r\nall images courtesy of jakob gomez##http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/dbsub/375274/2013-08-20/img_3_1376968191_6362f32dbcdeb5a80dc9ef3d8ec3b7eb.jpg@@\r\ngibooth Left##http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/jakob-gomez-gibooth-designboom01.jpg@@\r\ngibooth Red##http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/dbsub/375274/2013-08-20/img_11_1376968191_4f5d780cb097209c9ed3196bb2570cd5.jpg@@\r\ngibooth right ##http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/dbsub/375274/2013-08-20/img_5_1376968191_fe7af07d5a03bc0b47866f3f605b8c31.jp