azzaville-congo-IAD-designboom09.jpg@@\r\npan african games 2015 masterplan unveiled by IAD\r\nimage © independent architectural diplomacy##http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/pan-african-games-2015-brazzaville-congo-IAD-designboom10.jpg@@\r\npan african games 2015 masterplan unveiled by IAD\r\nimage © independent architectural diplomacy##http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/pan-african-games-2015-brazzaville-congo-IAD-designboom11.jpg@@\r\npan african games 2015 masterplan unveiled by IAD\r\nimage © independent architectural diplomacy##http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/pan-african-games-2015-brazzaville-congo-IAD-designboom12.jpg@@\r\npan african games 2015 masterplan unveiled by IAD\r\nimage © independent architectural diplomacy##http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/pan-african-games-2015-brazzaville-congo-IAD-designboom13.jpg@@\r\npan african games 2015 masterplan unveiled by IAD\r\nimage © independent architectural diplomacy##http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/pan-african-games-2015-brazzaville-congo-IAD-designboom14.jpg@@\r\npan african games 2015 masterplan unveiled by IAD\r\nimage © independent architectural diplomacy'),(298,'renzo piano：trentino新科学博物馆MUSE正式开放',' ## ##\r\n由著名建筑师renzo piano设计的意大利新trento科学博物馆，也称MUSE，于近日向公众开放。这座12,000平方米的空间将用\r\n无数种方式来探索人类与自然的关系。六层的空间追溯了整个自然历史，从高山带到世界其它地方，从微生物到生态群落，\r\n参观者会首先经过公共的研究实验室，然后在大量的教育展示中结束参观。MUSE将广泛的探讨意大利白云石山脉的形成，\r\n以及阿尔卑斯山脉的诞生——这些研究内容都反映在了建筑形式和构造上。倾斜的尖角和玻璃屋顶让人联想到周围的山脉。\r\n自然与建筑技术的对话也反映到体量组合与中庭的设计上，为展览带来超凡脱俗、身临其境的感受，同时卷曲的形式，白色\r\n建筑体量和大面积玻璃立面创造了360度的投影和互动数字媒体屏幕。出了室内充足的自然光照，建筑师还利用当地材料、对\r\n环境冲击较小的构造材料，使用包括竹子和雨水收集系统等可持续设计，来达到LEED绿色建筑最高认证的条件。这座博物馆还\r\n设有一个可伸缩的遮阳系统，太阳能光电板和低温探测器。 ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ## ','http://cn.designboom.com/cat/3/view/1892/renzo-piano%EF%BC%9Atrentino%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A6%86muse%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE.html','--- !ruby/object:Nokogiri::XML::Element {}\n','',1