多先进高效的透明材料相继出现，立面开窗变得更加灵活。因为建筑师可以用开窗来“取景”，用更巧妙的逻辑方法在建筑与\r\n环境之间建立联系，而不用去牺牲室内的私密性。##日期: 2011-12\r\n类型: 教育建筑\r\n方案阶段: 研究团队成员: nathalie frankowski, cruz garcia, wu dang shen\r\n位置: 中国, 北京 ','http://cn.designboom.com/cat/3/view/1117/wai-architecture-institute-of-optimistic-architectures.html','--- !ruby/object:Nokogiri::XML::Element {}\n','',1,2,13,'boom_cn',NULL,'\\/view\\/',NULL,'','2013-11-14','2013-11-14',''),(1156,'arquitectura-G: claudio椅','','http://cn.designboom.com/cat/4/view/1118/arquitectura-g-claudio%E6%A4%85.html','--- !ruby/object:Nokogiri::XML::Element {}\n','',1,2,13,'boom_cn',NULL,'\\/view\\/',NULL,'','2013-11-14','2013-11-14','/weblog/images/images_2/massimo/claudio01.jpg@@##/weblog/images/images_2/andrea/miscellaneous/arquitectura_G/claudio02.jpg@@当几把 \'claudio\'椅子水平排列时, 会产生消失点透视效果 ##/weblog/images/images_2/andrea/miscellaneous/arquitectura_G/claudio03.jpg@@堆叠排列##/weblog/images/images_2/andrea/miscellaneous/arquitectura_G/claudio04.jpg@@背靠背排列##/weblog/images/images_2/andrea/miscellaneous/arquitectura_G/claudio05.jpg@@\'claudio椅\'##/weblog/images/images_2/andrea/miscellaneous/arquitectura_G/claudio06.jpg@@围合成圆形大剧场##/weblog/images/images_2/andrea/miscellaneous/arquitectura_G/claudioa.jpg@@\'雅典学院\' by raphael（拉斐尔）##/weblog/images/images_2/andrea/miscellaneous/arquitectura_G/claudio08.jpg@@\'delights of the poet\' by giorgio de chirico'),(1157,'阿姆斯特丹标志性桥梁设计竞赛','','http://cn.designboom.com/cat/3/view/1116/%E9%98%BF%E5%A7%86%E6%96%AF%E7%89%B9%E4%B8%B9%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E6%80%A7%E6%A1%A5%E6%A2%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%AB%9E%E8%B5%9B.html','--- !ruby/object:Nokogiri::XML::Element {}\n','',1,2,13,'boom_cn',NULL,'\\/view\\/',NULL,'','2013-11-14','2013-11-14','/weblog/images/images_2/lauren/pedestrian%20bridge/pb01.jpg@@阿姆斯特丹步行桥\r\nall images courtesy of [AC-CA]##/weblog/images/images_2/lauren/pedestrian%20bridge/pb02.jpg@@室内##/weblog/images/images_2/lauren/pedestrian%20bridge/pb03.jpg@@夜景##/weblog/images/images_2/lauren/pedestrian%20bridge/pb04.jpg@@鸟瞰图##/weblog